name: Meet Elizabeth Bartusiak
body:
# So, Who IS Elizabeth, Anyway? # ![](https://scontent-ord1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xpt1/v/t1.0-9/10375492_1485615991713376_1411056303023213371_n.jpg?oh=f9e34e3bfce4286a39fde897109745a0&oe=5614141A) Hello! My name is Elizabeth Bartusiak. My favorite colors are orange and yellow because they are so bright and happy! Something you would not guess by looking at me is that I love to play basketball. Consequently, I am also a big fan of the Chicago Bulls. I play the violin and love to practice often. Last year, I even played for a wedding! Aside from running on the basketball court and making music, I love math. To me, math is like solving complex problems using nothing but a little bit of hope and a lot of shear logic! In the future, you will find me working with computer science to protect other people's cyber-security.

Kembray-Elizabeth Pollick

Made using: Khan Academy Computer Science.
